        "commit": {
          "message": "Chess Clock — beautiful timer for over-the-board play\n\n12 preset time controls (bullet, blitz, rapid, classical) with\nincrement support. Tap to switch, pause/resume, move counter,\nred time warning under 30s, tenths display under 20s. Top player\nrotated 180 degrees for face-to-face play. 202KB bundle, offline PWA.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
          "author": {
